data.title: Dr. Raed Falah Khalifa - Medics Index Member Profile
data.meta_description: Dr. Raed Falah Khalifa - Medics Index Member Profile - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Dr. Raed Falah Khalifa is an American citizen of Jordanian descent who works as the program director at AL Amal Maternity Hospital in Amman, Jordan. He received his medical degree from Cairo University in 2002 and completed his residency in obstetrics and gynecology at the University of Jordan Hospital. Dr. Khalifa is board certified in obstetrics and gynecology by the Jordan Medical Council and has over 15 years of experience in the field. He is fluent in Arabic, English, and French and specializes in obstetrics, gynecology, and fertility treatments.
